msg: Use a SortedMap for the data. The data was typed as Map<String, String> but every time we want to do something with it, it is converted to a TreeMap (impls. SortedMap).
- This is wasteful if the map is already a SortedMap.
- There is a lot code duplication to create the sorted maps.
